metadata.name: Beep Boop Toolbox #1
metadata.description: Toolboxes can be purchased with your newly acquired $BOOP tokens from the holding zone in order to start collecting tools. Once you have your toolbox, you will be able earn a boost in daily yield in the holding zone as long as you are staking your bot too. You can add up to three toolboxes per bot in the holding zone to earn more $BOOP for battle. each box yields 500 $BOOP a day. BeepBoopBotz.io
